里面发二次元的</p>\n<p>一年不会去几次旅游，若是吃饭拍个照什么的，我前阵子去打卡了几家网红店，发现发不出手，吃个饭有什么好发的...太尴尬了，也没钱没什么好晒的物品，当然也不爱运动，不爱看正经书</p>\n<p>求解求解</p>\n","last_modified":1698716050,"replies":16,"id":986952},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913","name":"apple","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913","title":"Apple","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","topics":24033,"footer":"","header":"设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。","title_alternative":"Apple","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913","stars":2769,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":184,"parent_node_name":"hardware"},"member":{"id":455124,"username":"pocarisweat","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/pocarisweat","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/fde40fc7441030ee57fb96b1b7c1deef?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/fde40fc7441030ee57fb96b1b7c1deef?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/fde40fc7441030ee57fb96b1b7c1deef?s=73&d=retro","created":1574580908,"last_modified":1690385804},"last_reply_by":"gps949","last_touched":1698717377,"title":"每次发布会都有人认为没新意，过去十年有哪些苹果产品让你觉得「有新意」？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/986943","created":1698715245,"deleted":0,"content":"","content_rendered":"","last_modified":1698715245,"replies":13,"id":986943},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913","name":"apple","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913","title":"Apple","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","topics":24033,"footer":"","header":"设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone<